{"title":"go语言函数","uid":"14f39d25edcfe947fd2b26042086ecb4","slug":"go语言函数","date":"2023-11-22T19:29:29.379Z","updated":"2023-11-22T19:29:29.381Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/go语言函数.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/6.jpg","content":"<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>函数是基本的代码块，用于执行一个任务。<br>Go 语言最少有个 main() 函数。<br>你可以通过函数来划分不同功能，逻辑上每个函数执行的是指定的任务。<br>函数声明告诉了编译器函数的名称，返回类型，和参数。<br>Go 语言标准库提供了多种可动用的内置的函数。例如，len()<br>函数可以接受不同类型参数并返回该类型的长度。如果我们传入的是字符串则返回字符串的长度，如果传入的是数组，则返回数组中包含的元素个数。</p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"函数定义\"><a href=\"#函数定义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"函数定义\"></a>函数定义</h1><p>函数定义格式如下：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">func function_name( [parameter list] ) [return_types] &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   函数体</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>函数定义解析：<br>func：函数由 func 开始声明<br>function_name：函数名称，参数列表和返回值类型构成了函数签名。<br>parameter<br>list：参数列表，参数就像一个占位符，当函数被调用时，你可以将值传递给参数，这个值被称为实际参数。参数列表指定的是参数类型、顺序、及参数个数。参数是可选的，也就是说函数也可以不包含参数。<br>return_types：返回类型，函数返回一列值。return_types<br>是该列值的数据类型。有些功能不需要返回值，这种情况下 return_types<br>不是必须的。<br>函数体：函数定义的代码集合。</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"实例\"><a href=\"#实例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实例\"></a>实例</h2>","text":" 函数是基本的代码块，用于执行一个任务。Go 语言最少有个 main() 函数。你可以通过函数来划分不同功能，逻辑上每个函数执行的是指定的任务。函数声明告诉了编...","permalink":"/post/go语言函数","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":568,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"GO","slug":"GO","count":7,"path":"api/categories/GO.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"GO","slug":"GO","count":7,"path":"api/tags/GO.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">函数定义</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实例</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"nnnpc","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/2.jpg","link":"/","description":"安全萌新","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"go语言变量作用域","uid":"52d57ca0884fcc119dcf3941a54c9365","slug":"go语言变量作用域","date":"2023-11-22T19:30:46.526Z","updated":"2023-11-22T19:30:46.527Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/go语言变量作用域.json","keywords":null,"cover